comments:
I noticed all the colors had the same last portion of the words, those being (she, lu, tho, and sa), and I used these to match the colors she(blue), lu(yellow), tho(red), and sa(purple). The first portions of the words also matched the shape of the patterns, once I was able to remember the names(wopi, buvi, gafi, zeti), I was able to learn it pretty easily.

I didn't use any paper or make any notes. I found the words, Zeti and Wopi to be much easier to remember for their paterns, then the words buvi and gafi.
